{
  "stem": "9728.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was not anymore any barracks, but they were huts.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were dug out in the ground.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And you walked in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was actually a hut.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And you were just laying down on the-- on the boards to sleep.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were there for about two, three weeks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Then they decided that they are going to make this camp in Kaufering, that they are going to make this a sick camp for sick people-- whatever they are going to do with the people.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Before they transport them to-- before they transport them to the crematorium, or whatever, this is going to be the camp where they're going to keep them.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "When they decided that they're going to make the-- the sick camp from-- from Kaufering, they send us away to another camp.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that camp was-- they had numbers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Now, that sick camp in Kaufering was called Camp Number Four.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They sent us to Camp Number Three.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "In Camp Number Three, this was already an established camp-- an established camp that we went out every morning to work.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Most of the people that they were in there were a-- a majority was-- were Lithuanian, from Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And Lithuanian Jews.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "There were a-- a sparkling--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--a sparkling of rations there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And some Poles.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What we did is we went out, and we dug bunkers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We dug for the-- for the German Luftwaffe, and for the-- for the military, and for the weapons and [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, this was now already the end of-- the end of 1944.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was the end of 1944.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was quite cold and snowy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I was always with my brother from one camp to the other one.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
